@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About GymWeb";
}

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>@ViewData["Title"]</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif; text-align: center;">

    <h1 style="color: white; margin-top: 40px;">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

    <p style="color: white; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 30px;">
        Welcome to GymWeb, where fitness meets grace, and well-being becomes a lifestyle.
        At GymWeb, we embody the essence of simplicity and elegance in the pursuit of a healthier, more fulfilling life.
    </p>

    <div class="container">
        <img src="/images/photo1.jpg" alt="Image 1" class="img-thumbnail" style="margin: 10px;">
        <img src="/images/photo2.jpg" alt="Image 2" class="img-thumbnail" style="margin: 10px;">
        <img src="/images/photo3.jpg" alt="Image 3" class="img-thumbnail" style="margin: 10px;">
    </div>

    <p style="color:white">
        Our philosophy revolves around simplicity and elegance. We believe that the journey to a healthier you doesn't need to be complicated. It starts with small, consistent steps and a positive mindset. That's why we provide a serene and welcoming environment where you can focus on your well-being without distractions.

        What sets GymWeb apart is our commitment to personalized fitness experiences. Our certified trainers are here to guide you, whether you're just starting your fitness journey or looking to enhance your current routine. We offer a variety of classes, from yoga and Pilates to high-intensity interval training, catering to diverse fitness preferences.

        As you embark on your fitness journey with GymWeb, you'll discover the joy of moving your body, the strength within you, and the support of a community that celebrates every achievement – big or small.

        Explore our state-of-the-art facilities, connect with like-minded individuals, and make fitness a part of your lifestyle. GymWeb is not just a gym; it's a destination where fitness meets grace, and your well-being becomes our priority.

        <br><br>

        <strong>Our Facilities:</strong> Discover a space equipped with cutting-edge technology and modern amenities to make your workout experience enjoyable and effective.

        <strong>Community Support:</strong> Join a community of individuals who share your passion for health and wellness. Engage in group activities, workshops, and events that foster a sense of belonging.

        <strong>Wellness Programs:</strong> Beyond traditional workouts, GymWeb offers holistic wellness programs, including nutrition guidance, mindfulness sessions, and personalized fitness plans.

        <strong>Membership Benefits:</strong> Enjoy exclusive perks as a GymWeb member, including access to special classes, discounts on merchandise, and priority scheduling for personal training sessions.

        We invite you to take the first step towards a healthier, more vibrant life at GymWeb. Join us on this transformative journey, and let fitness become an integral part of your story.
    </p>

</body>
</html>
